OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FCommunity pharmacists are under severe
OL,7,Ffinancial pressure due to an "utterly
OL,8,Fbroken" payment system, experts have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FA mismatch between the price of some
OL,12,Fmedicines and the amount that
OL,13,Fpharmacists are reimbursed by the
OL,14,FGovernment means that many are making
OL,15,Fa loss, pharmacy leaders said.
OL,17,FThe National Pharmacy Association
OL,18,F(NPA) said that many community
OL,19,Fpharmacists are paying out of their
OL,20,Fown pockets to ensure patients get the
OL,21,Fmedicines they need.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@GO]
