OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FIt said that the health system is
OL,7,Funderpaying pharmacies for medicines
OL,8,Fby as much as #75 a pack.
OL,10,FOne pharmacist described how is can
OL,11,Fmake losses of #1,000 a month due to
OL,12,Fthe mismatch in prices.
OL,14,FThe NPA said that pharmacies are
OL,15,Fclosing in "record numbers" due to
OL,16,Ffinancial pressures.
OL,18,FOlivier Picard, a pharmacist in
OL,19,FBerkshire, told the PA news agency
OL,20,Fthat the discrepancy between the
OL,21,Fprices "huge".
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@[O]}D@HOU}D@MO]
