OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,F"This is affecting us enormously," he
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,F"The number of products that we cannot
OL,10,Fpurchase under the reimbursement price
OL,11,Fis increasing and increasing, and the
OL,12,Fprices that we are seeing... the
OL,13,Fdiscrepancy is so huge.
OL,15,F"A couple of months ago, we were
OL,16,Flosing #20 a packet on a medicine for
OL,17,Fstroke prevention. The next month, we
OL,18,Flost money on something that you give
OL,19,Fas an antidepressant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@bO]qD@AOUwD@AOU
