OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,F"Sometimes it'll be a few pence,
OL,7,Fsometimes it'll be several pounds.
OL,9,F"There are some months where I am out
OL,10,Fof pocket by #1,000 pounds per
OL,11,Fpharmacy ` I have got four pharmacies.
OL,13,F"It is not a sustainable model. It is
OL,14,Fnot something that I can continue
OL,15,Fdoing.
OL,17,F"Every month we dispense at a loss for
OL,18,Fdozens of medications."
