OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FThe NPA, which represents independent
OL,7,Fcommunity pharmacies in the UK, said
OL,8,Ffinancial pressure on pharmacies has
OL,9,Fforced 1,500 to have closed
OL,10,Fpermanently in England in the past
OL,11,Fdecade.
OL,13,FThe NPA conducted a snapshot survey on
OL,14,FOctober 7 of drug prices from pharmacy
OL,15,Fwholesalers and compared it to how
OL,16,Fmuch pharmacies are reimbursed through
OL,17,Fthe NHS Drug Tariff, funded by the
OL,18,FDepartment of Health and Social Care.
OL,19,FThe NPA found:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
