OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FPharmacies cannot stop supplying
OL,7,Fmedicines because of cost because this
OL,8,Fwould put them in breach of their
OL,9,Fcontract with the health service,
OL,10,Fexperts said.
OL,12,FEarlier this year an NPA poll revealed
OL,13,Fthat 85% of community pharmacies say
OL,14,Fthat they "often" make a net loss on
OL,15,FNHS prescribing.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the survey of around 500
OL,18,Fsmall independent community
OL,19,Fpharmacies, also found 36% feared they
OL,20,Fwill be forced to close within a year
OL,21,Fdue to financial pressures.
