OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FPaul Rees, NPA chief executive, added:
OL,7,F"It is nothing short of a national
OL,8,Fscandal that pharmacies have to dig
OL,9,Fdeep into their own pockets just to
OL,10,Fcover the cost of basic medicines that
OL,11,Fthey dispense to patients in need of
OL,12,Ftreatment. No other health
OL,13,Fprofessional would be asked subsidise
OL,14,Fa key NHS service.
OL,16,F"The system for funding the medicines
OL,17,Fupon which millions of patients rely
OL,18,Fis utterly broken.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
