OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,F"Pharmacists are left tearing their
OL,7,Fhair out at a system that simply
OL,8,Fdoesn't cover the cost of medicines
OL,9,Fthey are forced to buy on the open
OL,10,Fmarket, which make up the vast
OL,11,Fmajority of their workload.
OL,13,F"This pressure has led pharmacy owners
OL,14,Fto desperate measures to keep their
OL,15,Fpharmacies open for their local
OL,16,Fcommunity, including borrowing from
OL,17,Ffamily, raiding pension savings and
OL,18,Feven in some cases remortgaging their
OL,19,Fhomes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
