CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F312A1729082353
OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,F"We share the Government's ambitions
OL,7,Fto expand the role of pharmacies but
OL,8,Fthis cannot happen whilst they are
OL,9,Fbeing forced to closing at record
OL,10,Fnumbers by chronic underfunding.
OL,12,F"The Government must step in now to
OL,13,Fhalt pharmacy closures, fix the broken
OL,14,Ffunding system and deliver a new deal
OL,15,Ffor pharmacies which will end the
OL,16,Fterrible toll of closures and cuts to
OL,17,Fservices."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@JO]
