OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,FLouise Ansari, chief executive of
OL,7,FHealthwatch England, said: "These
OL,8,Ffindings are worrying, with community
OL,9,Fpharmacies already facing multiple
OL,10,Fchallenges, including closures and
OL,11,Fshortages of prescription medication.
OL,13,F"Community pharmacists provide a
OL,14,Flifeline to patients, especially those
OL,15,Fwith chronic health conditions, and
OL,16,Fplay a huge role in alleviating the
OL,17,Fstrain on GPs.
OL,26,@oD@\OUuD@AOU
