PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F312A1729082353
OL,3,CCommunity pharmacies 'footing the
OL,4,Cbill' for many NHS drugs
OL,6,F"The more pharmacies that close, the
OL,7,Fmore people will be forced to travel
OL,8,Ffurther or risk not getting the
OL,9,Fadvice, care and medications they
OL,10,Fneed, when they need them.
OL,12,F"We have called for a national
OL,13,Fevaluation of pharmacy funding, and
OL,14,Fthe Government has announced that it
OL,15,Fwill look into this. These findings
OL,16,Fonly underscore why the review needs
OL,17,Fto happen as soon as possible."
