OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "This government
OL,8,Finherited a broken NHS but is
OL,9,Fcommitted to expanding the role of
OL,10,Fpharmacists, making better use of the
OL,11,Fskills of pharmacists and pharmacy
OL,12,Ftechnicians.
OL,14,F"We already reimburse community
OL,15,Fpharmacies for what they spend on
OL,16,Fdrugs and provide additional funding
OL,17,Ffor the services they provide. There
OL,18,Fare also safeguards in place if
OL,19,Fpurchase prices for a given drug
OL,20,Fincrease."
